									<img class="assignedTeamMember-img" src="./icons/profile.png" alt="teamMember">
									<img class="assignedTeamMember-img" src="./icons/profile.png" alt="teamMember">
								</div>
								<div class="dueDate-container">
									<h3 class="paragraph-3">00:40 25/02/2021</h3>
								</div>
							</div>
							<input class="btnEdit btnIcon" type="button">
						</div>


					</div>
				</div>

				<!--here start the verify section of the sprint backlog-->
				<div class="crossAxisList">
					<h3 class="paragraph-3"><b class="focus">Sprint Backlog</b> - To verify</h3>
					<div id="sprintBacklogId" class="crossAxisList-item__container dragSprintBacklogContainer">

						<div id="sprintBacklogId" class="crossAxisList-item dragSprintBacklog" draggable = "true">
							<p class="paragraph-3">
								If there is one task that has to be <b class="focus">verified</b> by a developer, will be moved to the "<b class="focus">working</b>" column if is finally <b class="focus">aproved</b>, will be placed in "<b class="focus">Done</b>" column.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div id="sprintBacklogId" class="crossAxisList-item dragSprintBacklog" draggable = "true">
							<div class="info-container">
								<h3 class="paragraph-2">Function name</h3>
								<p class="paragraph-3">
									This is a small description of a <b class="focus">function</b> in the product and its <b class="focus">details</b>.
								</p>
								<div class="assignedTeamMember-container">
									<img class="assignedTeamMember-img" src="./icons/profile.png" alt="teamMember">
									<img class="assignedTeamMember-img" src="./icons/profile.png" alt="teamMember">
