								<b class="focus">Tasks</b> pile up over when they're <b class="focus">done</b>. They're <b class="focus">removed</b> at the <b class="focus">end</b> of the <b class="focus">sprint</b>. Sometimes we remove some or all during a <b class="focus">sprint</b> if there are a lot of <b class="focus">tasks</b>.
							</p>
						</div>

